description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Bacillus ananas; Bacterium ananas; Erwinia ananas; Erwinia ananatis; Erwinia ananus; Erwinia herbicola var. ananas; Erwinia uredovora; Pantoea ananas; Pectobacterium ananas; Xanthomonas uredovorus.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
